      "amount": ""
    }
  ],
  "method": [
    "Take a skillet, and heat oil, and add the pepper, onion, cumin, and",
    "garlic—sizzle for 8-10 minutes.",
    "When the vegetables are golden and soft, add tomato purée and",
    "paprika, then cook for about 1 min.",
    "Add rice.",
    "Pour stock in it, then cover. Bring it to boil.",
    "Lower the heat, then cook for around 10 minutes.",
    "Turn down the heat and keep it covered for another 10 minutes.",
    "To serve immediately, add spring onions and coriander.",
    "To serve it later, cool down the rice, then refry it before serving. Then",
    "add spring onions and coriander."
